1
00:00:45,960 --> 00:00:47,560
He loves you to his very core.

2
00:00:49,440 --> 00:00:52,160
Even if it meant losing his mind.

3
00:00:53,040 --> 00:00:54,440
He did lose his mind.

4
00:00:55,400 --> 00:00:58,040
But you turned him from a demon into a god.

5
00:00:58,320 --> 00:01:01,040
He didn't become a monster that plagued the world,

6
00:01:01,040 --> 00:01:02,900
because he wanted to protect you.

7
00:01:03,520 --> 00:01:04,360
To guard you.

8
00:01:05,040 --> 00:01:06,100
The you of the past,

9
00:01:06,760 --> 00:01:08,020
the you of the present.

10
00:01:08,440 --> 00:01:10,920
From beginning to end, you are just you.

11
00:01:11,360 --> 00:01:13,280
When you remember everything,

12
00:01:13,560 --> 00:01:14,960
you will understand him,

13
00:01:15,640 --> 00:01:16,720
know him,

14
00:01:16,920 --> 00:01:17,960
and become him.

15
00:01:18,560 --> 00:01:19,200
Thank you,

16
00:01:19,680 --> 00:01:21,080
for telling me my story.

17
00:01:22,840 --> 00:01:24,240
Thank you and Yueying,

18
00:01:24,320 --> 00:01:27,850
for staying with him through his thousand years of loneliness.

19
00:01:34,440 --> 00:01:35,500
What is happening?

20
00:01:38,280 --> 00:01:39,280
Sister Qingluan,

21
00:01:39,720 --> 00:01:42,780
my Spirit Bead suddenly flew toward the Spirit Spring.

22
00:02:10,320 --> 00:02:11,160
Ling'er.

23
00:02:11,840 --> 00:02:13,370
It's been a thousand years.

24
00:02:13,760 --> 00:02:15,000
I gave up everything,

25
00:02:15,480 --> 00:02:17,140
and finally brought you back.

26
00:02:25,800 --> 00:02:26,600
Yunyuan.

27
00:02:27,960 --> 00:02:28,760
Yunyuan.

28
00:02:30,840 --> 00:02:31,480
Ling'er.

29
00:02:31,560 --> 00:02:32,090
Yunyuan.

30
00:02:32,400 --> 00:02:33,200
Yunyuan.

31
00:02:33,280 --> 00:02:33,960
No.

32
00:02:34,440 --> 00:02:35,440
Don't pull it out.

33
00:02:35,640 --> 00:02:36,170
Yunyuan.

34
00:02:36,280 --> 00:02:36,960
No.

35
00:02:37,280 --> 00:02:37,960
Don't!

36
00:02:38,200 --> 00:02:39,320
I beg you.

37
00:02:40,240 --> 00:02:42,040
Yunyuan.

38
00:02:46,760 --> 00:02:47,290
Ling'er.

39
00:02:49,720 --> 00:02:50,600
Yunyuan.

40
00:02:51,840 --> 00:02:53,480
My Yunyuan.

41
00:02:55,040 --> 00:02:56,360
Yunyuan.

42
00:02:57,120 --> 00:02:58,280
I am Yunyuan.

43
00:02:59,360 --> 00:03:00,640
I am your Yunyuan.

44
00:03:09,400 --> 00:03:10,440
You're okay.

45
00:03:15,080 --> 00:03:16,160
You're okay.

46
00:03:16,320 --> 00:03:18,280
I'm so glad you're okay.

47
00:03:19,280 --> 00:03:20,280
I'm fine.

48
00:03:20,960 --> 00:03:21,760
Ling'er.

49
00:03:22,360 --> 00:03:23,200
My Ling'er.

50
00:03:24,840 --> 00:03:25,640
Yunyuan.

51
00:03:26,280 --> 00:03:27,880
I had a dream.

52
00:03:29,400 --> 00:03:31,200
A very long dream.

53
00:03:32,480 --> 00:03:34,280
You fool.

54
00:03:34,880 --> 00:03:36,640
How could you do this?

55
00:03:36,880 --> 00:03:37,560
What if...

56
00:03:39,800 --> 00:03:41,280
I mean, what if...

57
00:03:41,560 --> 00:03:45,400
what if I woke up and I was all alone?

58
00:03:45,880 --> 00:03:46,680
Ling'er.

59
00:03:47,400 --> 00:03:49,440
I would never let you be alone.

60
00:03:50,880 --> 00:03:52,640
Let me see your wound.

61
00:03:59,520 --> 00:04:01,840
It must really hurt.

62
00:04:03,720 --> 00:04:04,520
It doesn't.

63
00:04:06,440 --> 00:04:07,240
Ling'er.

64
00:04:09,760 --> 00:04:11,160
It was all worth it.

65
00:04:11,960 --> 00:04:13,360
You dummy.

66
00:04:14,040 --> 00:04:15,440
You pulled out your Heart Scale.

67
00:04:15,440 --> 00:04:17,240
How could it not hurt?

68
00:04:20,000 --> 00:04:22,280
I've never met anyone as foolish as you.

69
00:04:28,720 --> 00:04:30,280
I'm so afraid that right now,

70
00:04:30,280 --> 00:04:31,720
all of this,

71
00:04:33,240 --> 00:04:35,640
is just a dream I've had countless times.

72
00:04:41,840 --> 00:04:42,570
Does it hurt?

73
00:04:46,159 --> 00:04:47,890
Do you still think it's a dream?

74
00:05:02,640 --> 00:05:04,640
Alright, that's enough, you two.

75
00:05:04,640 --> 00:05:06,170
There are people watching.

76
00:05:08,640 --> 00:05:09,570
I have business.

77
00:05:10,000 --> 00:05:12,660
I wouldn't be here torturing myself otherwise.

78
00:05:13,760 --> 00:05:14,560
Ling'er.

79
00:05:17,560 --> 00:05:18,200
Ling'er,

80
00:05:18,280 --> 00:05:19,600
now that your memory is back,

81
00:05:19,600 --> 00:05:21,640
why is your spiritual power still so weak?

82
00:05:21,640 --> 00:05:23,400
As a dignified Princess of the Dragon Clan,

83
00:05:23,400 --> 00:05:25,080
you shouldn't be this weak.

84
00:05:25,480 --> 00:05:26,610
The Dragon Lord said

85
00:05:26,680 --> 00:05:28,080
that once the Spirit Pearl was restored,

86
00:05:28,080 --> 00:05:30,080
Ling'er would recover her true form and memory.

87
00:05:30,080 --> 00:05:31,400
I don't know either.

88
00:05:32,159 --> 00:05:33,760
But a mark appeared on my arm.

89
00:05:35,159 --> 00:05:38,360
Don't tell me you're going through a second growth spurt?

90
00:05:41,280 --> 00:05:43,810
Ling'er, did you really get your memory back?

91
00:05:43,880 --> 00:05:45,520
Yes, I remember everything.

92
00:05:45,680 --> 00:05:47,280
Diyun, long time no see.

93
00:05:47,880 --> 00:05:48,760
You look...

94
00:05:49,200 --> 00:05:50,760
exactly the same as before.

95
00:05:51,240 --> 00:05:52,640
What difference would there be?

96
00:05:52,640 --> 00:05:54,560
I just remembered the past.

97
00:05:54,880 --> 00:05:56,200
Sorry, Diyun.

98
00:05:56,200 --> 00:05:57,680
I tricked you twice.

99
00:05:58,280 --> 00:05:59,240
Twice?

100
00:05:59,280 --> 00:06:01,080
When you came to break off the engagement,

101
00:06:01,080 --> 00:06:03,400
I disguised myself as a maid to tease you.

102
00:06:04,080 --> 00:06:06,840
And that guard from the Heaven Clan who beat you up?

103
00:06:06,840 --> 00:06:07,600
That was me.

104
00:06:08,560 --> 00:06:09,840
I knew it.

105
00:06:10,080 --> 00:06:11,720
So your petty personality

106
00:06:11,720 --> 00:06:12,980
existed back then too.

107
00:06:13,560 --> 00:06:14,480
Nice work.

108
00:06:16,160 --> 00:06:16,690
Ling'er.

109
00:06:16,840 --> 00:06:18,440
Find time to go back to the Dragon Clan.

110
00:06:18,440 --> 00:06:20,400
The Dragon Lord might know the reason.

111
00:06:20,400 --> 00:06:20,880
Okay.

112
00:06:21,040 --> 00:06:22,770
I happen to miss my father, too.

113
00:06:27,040 --> 00:06:28,560
The Lord's mark

114
00:06:29,040 --> 00:06:30,560
has finally appeared.

115
00:06:31,280 --> 00:06:32,800
The day of the Lord's

116
00:06:33,040 --> 00:06:35,400
descent is near.

117
00:06:39,760 --> 00:06:40,680
Grand Protector.

118
00:06:40,680 --> 00:06:41,800
But the Demon Lord

119
00:06:41,800 --> 00:06:43,330
has sent new instructions.

120
00:06:46,840 --> 00:06:48,480
The Lord is visionary.

121
00:06:48,960 --> 00:06:50,520
Thousands of years ago,

122
00:06:50,520 --> 00:06:52,480
he already prepared a backup plan.

123
00:06:53,600 --> 00:06:57,880
Now that the Spirit Pearl and the Soul have merged,

124
00:06:58,480 --> 00:06:59,880
if we don't act now,

125
00:07:00,240 --> 00:07:01,640
when will we?

126
00:07:03,080 --> 00:07:04,440
They've merged?

127
00:07:05,960 --> 00:07:07,880
Then I will lead men to Kunmi immediately

128
00:07:07,880 --> 00:07:09,080
to snatch the Spirit Pearl back.

129
00:07:09,080 --> 00:07:09,640
Wait.

130
00:07:12,280 --> 00:07:13,240
I'm warning you.

131
00:07:13,800 --> 00:07:15,360
Do not act without orders.

132
00:07:16,280 --> 00:07:19,140
If you disrupt the Lord's ten-thousand-year plan,

133
00:07:19,280 --> 00:07:20,610
be careful that the Lord

134
00:07:22,240 --> 00:07:23,760
doesn't destroy you.

135
00:07:26,680 --> 00:07:27,280
So...

136
00:07:28,560 --> 00:07:30,640
we don't need to snatch the Spirit Pearl?

137
00:07:30,640 --> 00:07:34,080
The Lord's goal was never the Spirit Pearl.

138
00:07:35,200 --> 00:07:36,360
The Lord wants...

139
00:07:38,159 --> 00:07:39,080
Forget it.

140
00:07:39,240 --> 00:07:41,640
You wouldn't understand even if I told you.

141
00:07:42,080 --> 00:07:42,840
Remember.

142
00:07:43,600 --> 00:07:45,640
Do not do anything unnecessary.

143
00:07:49,080 --> 00:07:50,560
When the time is right,

144
00:07:51,040 --> 00:07:52,680
you will know.

145
00:07:54,520 --> 00:07:55,080
Yes.

146
00:07:59,080 --> 00:08:01,280
What should I give Yunyuan?

147
00:08:08,680 --> 00:08:09,960
With my blood,

148
00:08:10,640 --> 00:08:12,770
I seek the spirits of heaven and earth.

149
00:08:13,080 --> 00:08:14,740
The Imperial Heaven and Earth

150
00:08:15,040 --> 00:08:17,040
answer to the Water Dragon's Chant.

151
00:08:22,240 --> 00:08:24,160
You stripped your scales and bones for me.

152
00:08:24,160 --> 00:08:26,240
I will use the blood from my heart

153
00:08:26,440 --> 00:08:28,100
to make a jade pendant for you.

154
00:08:29,160 --> 00:08:31,490
Later, I will forge a suit of armor for you.

155
00:08:32,000 --> 00:08:35,480
My Heart Scale will become the breastplate on your armor.

156
00:08:35,840 --> 00:08:36,880
To keep you safe

157
00:08:37,400 --> 00:08:38,799
and make you invincible.

158
00:08:44,680 --> 00:08:46,480
Ling'er, time to get up.

159
00:08:46,560 --> 00:08:47,080
Brother.

160
00:08:47,080 --> 00:08:47,720
Ling'er.

161
00:08:47,840 --> 00:08:49,760
Something's wrong.

162
00:08:52,080 --> 00:08:52,680
Ling'er!

163
00:08:53,360 --> 00:08:54,200
Ling'er!

164
00:08:54,880 --> 00:08:55,680
What's wrong with Ling'er?

165
00:08:55,680 --> 00:08:56,160
Quick.

166
00:08:56,680 --> 00:08:57,480
Go, quickly.

167
00:09:04,400 --> 00:09:05,440
When it comes to acting,

168
00:09:05,440 --> 00:09:06,840
if we claim second place,

169
00:09:07,040 --> 00:09:08,760
no one dares claim first.

170
00:09:28,480 --> 00:09:29,040
Ling'er.

171
00:09:29,760 --> 00:09:30,440
Yunyuan.

172
00:09:31,400 --> 00:09:33,000
This path of ours,

173
00:09:33,840 --> 00:09:36,040
you've walked it with such difficulty.

174
00:09:36,760 --> 00:09:37,800
This time,

175
00:09:39,080 --> 00:09:40,480
let me walk towards you.

176
00:09:51,040 --> 00:09:51,840
Ling'er.

177
00:09:53,240 --> 00:09:56,770
You actually made a jade pendant for me with your heart's blood.

178
00:09:57,280 --> 00:09:59,080
Yeah. Do you like it?

179
00:10:00,280 --> 00:10:02,140
As long as it's from you, Ling'er,

180
00:10:02,880 --> 00:10:04,040
I love it all.

181
00:10:05,200 --> 00:10:06,440
Will you marry me?

182
00:10:07,840 --> 00:10:09,370
It is what my heart desires.

183
00:10:10,080 --> 00:10:11,680
I could ask for nothing more.

184
00:10:12,400 --> 00:10:13,680
For every lifetime,

185
00:10:14,880 --> 00:10:16,340
I will marry no one but you.

186
00:10:31,680 --> 00:10:32,520
Qingluan.

187
00:10:33,160 --> 00:10:35,400
Ling'er's spiritual power is dissipating.

188
00:10:35,400 --> 00:10:36,860
Take good care of Ling'er.

189
00:10:36,920 --> 00:10:38,850
I'm going back to the Dragon Tribe.

190
00:10:38,960 --> 00:10:39,880
Don't worry, Brother.

191
00:10:39,880 --> 00:10:42,810
Yueying and I will protect Kunmi and Sister-in-law.

192
00:10:44,880 --> 00:10:45,600
Ling'er.

193
00:10:45,880 --> 00:10:46,760
Are you bored?

194
00:10:46,960 --> 00:10:48,240
While Brother Yunyuan is away,

195
00:10:48,240 --> 00:10:49,640
I'll take you out to play.

196
00:10:50,520 --> 00:10:51,650
Morning, Qingluan.

197
00:10:52,000 --> 00:10:52,880
I'm going to find Ling'er.

198
00:10:52,880 --> 00:10:53,360
Hey!

199
00:10:53,480 --> 00:10:54,400
Get back here.

200
00:10:54,680 --> 00:10:55,880
Ling'er hasn't been well lately.

201
00:10:55,880 --> 00:10:57,440
You are not allowed to disturb her.

202
00:10:57,440 --> 00:10:58,880
Not well how?

203
00:10:59,880 --> 00:11:01,360
She can't condense her spiritual power.

204
00:11:01,360 --> 00:11:03,290
She's weak all over and lethargic.

205
00:11:05,080 --> 00:11:08,080
Those symptoms... certainly don't sound good.

206
00:11:09,960 --> 00:11:11,220
Then where is Yunyuan?

207
00:11:11,800 --> 00:11:13,660
Didn't he notice what's going on?

208
00:11:13,840 --> 00:11:15,480
Brother did notice something was wrong.

209
00:11:15,480 --> 00:11:17,360
That's why he left to find a cure.

210
00:11:17,760 --> 00:11:18,880
I also looked for

211
00:11:18,880 --> 00:11:21,410
many skilled healers in Kunmi to check on her,

212
00:11:21,480 --> 00:11:23,360
but none could find the cause.

213
00:11:29,440 --> 00:11:30,240
Well?

214
00:11:40,960 --> 00:11:42,320
Hey, what are you doing?

215
00:11:42,680 --> 00:11:43,610
Don't touch her!

216
00:11:46,000 --> 00:11:47,480
There is something wrong with Ling'er's left arm.

217
00:11:47,480 --> 00:11:49,480
It's absorbing my spiritual power.

218
00:11:49,680 --> 00:11:50,680
Step out for a moment.

219
00:11:50,680 --> 00:11:52,340
I need to check Ling'er's arm.

220
00:12:08,360 --> 00:12:09,480
On Ling'er's left arm,

221
00:12:09,480 --> 00:12:11,610
there is a golden dragon-shaped mark.

222
00:12:12,080 --> 00:12:13,400
A golden dragon mark?

223
00:12:15,760 --> 00:12:16,320
This is bad.

224
00:12:16,320 --> 00:12:17,480
I must return to the Heavenly Tribe

225
00:12:17,480 --> 00:12:18,760
to find Lord Yanxi.

226
00:12:18,840 --> 00:12:20,160
You can go back to the Heavenly Tribe?

227
00:12:20,160 --> 00:12:21,480
I thought you couldn't go back.

228
00:12:21,480 --> 00:12:22,560
I have my ways.

229
00:12:22,560 --> 00:12:23,600
Don't worry about it.

230
00:12:23,600 --> 00:12:24,960
Just wait for your brother to return.

231
00:12:24,960 --> 00:12:25,760
If he has no solution,

232
00:12:25,760 --> 00:12:26,880
wait for me to come back.

233
00:12:26,880 --> 00:12:27,480
Remember,

234
00:12:27,760 --> 00:12:29,280
you must keep your brother calm.

235
00:12:29,280 --> 00:12:30,880
His backlash is already unstable.

236
00:12:30,880 --> 00:12:31,680
Diyun!

237
00:12:33,280 --> 00:12:34,810
Can't you say it all at once?

238
00:12:36,160 --> 00:12:39,080
We've been neighbors for so long, after all.

239
00:12:39,360 --> 00:12:41,690
I've heard a little about your situation.

240
00:12:42,080 --> 00:12:44,080
This journey won't be easy, will it?

241
00:12:46,600 --> 00:12:49,080
Some people are worth it.

242
00:12:50,480 --> 00:12:52,680
But you are destined to receive no response.

243
00:12:52,680 --> 00:12:54,040
Not all love

244
00:12:54,480 --> 00:12:55,800
requires a response.

245
00:12:57,280 --> 00:12:59,040
Nor does all sacrifice

246
00:12:59,640 --> 00:13:00,680
require a return.

247
00:13:04,040 --> 00:13:04,960
Back then,

248
00:13:05,480 --> 00:13:07,080
to break off the engagement,

249
00:13:07,560 --> 00:13:09,640
I didn't hesitate to ruin her reputation

250
00:13:09,640 --> 00:13:12,500
and make her the laughingstock of the Three Realms.

251
00:13:13,680 --> 00:13:15,080
When she was mine,

252
00:13:15,360 --> 00:13:16,890
I treated her like nothing.

253
00:13:19,000 --> 00:13:20,280
Only after losing her

254
00:13:21,080 --> 00:13:22,480
did I regret it.

255
00:13:25,600 --> 00:13:26,480
When love

256
00:13:27,280 --> 00:13:28,480
outweighs guilt,

257
00:13:30,000 --> 00:13:30,960
it is arsenic,

258
00:13:32,440 --> 00:13:33,400
and also honey.

259
00:13:42,560 --> 00:13:44,360
Take good care of Ling'er for me.

260
00:13:49,760 --> 00:13:50,240
My Lord.

261
00:13:51,200 --> 00:13:51,720
My Lord.

262
00:13:52,280 --> 00:13:54,280
Do you really intend to return to the Heavenly Tribe in this mortal body now?

263
00:13:54,280 --> 00:13:54,880
Let go.

264
00:13:54,960 --> 00:13:55,640
My Lord.

265
00:13:56,080 --> 00:13:56,680
Or perhaps,

266
00:13:56,680 --> 00:13:57,840
I'll report to the Empress first

267
00:13:57,840 --> 00:13:59,080
and sound out the Emperor.

268
00:13:59,080 --> 00:14:00,480
Maybe the Emperor's anger has subsided.

269
00:14:00,480 --> 00:14:01,940
Let's just go back quietly

270
00:14:02,080 --> 00:14:03,840
and apologize properly to the Emperor.

271
00:14:03,840 --> 00:14:05,280
Father Emperor is the Lord of Heaven and Earth.

272
00:14:05,280 --> 00:14:07,360
His word is law and cannot be changed at will.

273
00:14:07,360 --> 00:14:08,560
You are forbidden from telling Mother Empress about this.

274
00:14:08,560 --> 00:14:10,890
I don't want her to worry about me anymore.

275
00:14:11,040 --> 00:14:11,960
My Lord.

276
00:14:12,120 --> 00:14:13,920
The ninety-nine steps of the Stairway to Heaven.

277
00:14:13,920 --> 00:14:14,960
Every step is deadly.

278
00:14:14,960 --> 00:14:16,280
Every pace is a tribulation.

279
00:14:16,280 --> 00:14:18,840
One misstep means your soul will be destroyed, My Lord.

280
00:14:18,840 --> 00:14:19,560
Let go.

281
00:14:19,800 --> 00:14:21,400
This is the only way to save Ling'er.

282
00:14:21,400 --> 00:14:23,440
Do you want me to just watch her die?

283
00:14:24,080 --> 00:14:25,440
What is so good about her

284
00:14:25,440 --> 00:14:28,770
that makes you risk the destruction of your soul to save her?

285
00:14:30,280 --> 00:14:31,480
She is my friend.

286
00:14:32,040 --> 00:14:33,440
She is the woman I love.

287
